{"tid":1823952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國上議院議員：促英方盡快制裁警隊高層及官員","createTime":"2020-01-14T05:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T12:56:56.000Z","uid":125168,"like":464,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"36411131bf28d76b1565f0463555ad4a1d62ad02","tid":1823952,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:40:58.000Z","msg":"【🇬🇧 英國戰線｜上議院議員撰文：促英方盡快制裁警隊高層及官員】<br />\n<br />\n英國今月底正式脫歐，英國上議院議員Lord Alton今日在具影響力的英國國會刊物《The House》撰文，表示過去一直香港面對北京「新文革」步步進逼，監控城市、打壓異見人士等無日無之，可見香港是自由世界的新戰線，認為英國新一年應以優先處理中國及香港問題。<br />\n<br />\n他公開促請英國政府就香港警察濫暴問題，向黑警及官員實施制裁，當中警隊高層及相關官員由於血腥鎮壓直接有關，故應是首批被制裁的目標。<br />\n<br />\n其實，保守黨早於去年10月1日已經承諾，脫歐後將針對打壓人權的行徑落實《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》（Magnitsky style sanctions），而背後有班英國手足「攬炒團隊」默默幫手遊說。<br />\n<br />\n攬炒團隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://standwithhk.org/about/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstandwithhk.org%2Fabout%2F&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHEkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=50c94348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://standwithhk.org/about/</a><br />\n<br />\n============<br />\n💰支持眾志 <a href=\"http://www.demosisto.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.demosisto.hk%2Fdonation&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHEkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=f716bd00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.demosisto.hk/donation</a>"},{"pid":"2949b0f1ea7dcb679e99e08bd04cefc60e7f878d","tid":1823952,"uid":125168,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8vy796.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8vy796.jpg&h=0342bbd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3787447229ca9f7cb1cbbb34e5079dff90315ce","tid":1823952,"uid":125168,"like":78,"dislike":2,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"英國係廢，但笑日落帝國係無用，逼佢地做嘢先有用，得閒笑不如幫手打英國戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e218258b5f969074a6694ffcce9d01d90481685","tid":1823952,"u